   20: -module(ets_property_test_SUITE).
   21: 
   22: -include_lib("common_test/include/ct.hrl").
   23: 
   24: -compile(export_all).
   25: -compile(nowarn_export_all).
   26: 
   27: all() -> [
   28:           first_case,
   29:           next_case,
   30:           last_case,
   31:           prev_case
   32:     ].
   33: 
   34: init_per_suite(Config) ->
   35:     ct_property_test:init_per_suite(Config).
   36: 
   37: end_per_suite(Config) ->
   38:     Config.
   39: 
   40: first_case(Config) ->
   41:     do_proptest(prop_first, Config).
   42: 
   43: next_case(Config) ->
   44:     do_proptest(prop_next, Config).
   45: 
   46: last_case(Config) ->
   47:     do_proptest(prop_last, Config).
   48: 
   49: prev_case(Config) ->
   50:     do_proptest(prop_prev, Config).
   51: 
   52: do_proptest(Prop, Config) ->
   53:     ct_property_test:quickcheck(
   54:         ets_prop:Prop(),
   55:         Config).
